    <sprite
    name="A"> / <sprite index=53> Move Left

    <sprite name="D"> / <sprite index=54>
    Move Right



    <sprite name="Shift"> Run Faster

    <sprite name="Space">
    Jump (Land) & Swim Up (Sea)

    <sprite name="Ctrl"> Dive Down (Sea)



    Actions:

    <sprite
    index=1> Primary Action (Use Tool & Attack)

    <sprite index=3> Secondary Action
    (Aim)

    <sprite name="R"> Repair Boat or Equipment



    Interactions:

    <sprite
    name="E"> Pick-up things, open things, & talk to AI parrot

    <sprite name="F">
    Use Tool or Interact with objects



    Menu:

    <sprite name="Esc"> Pause
    Game & Open Menu





    - Controller (Xbox & PlayStation)

    Movement:

